<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْغَاشِيَةِ}</span> ... القِيَامَةِ تَغْشَى النَّاسَ بِأَهْوَالِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاشِعَةٌ}</span> ... ذَلِيلَةٌ مُنْكَسِرَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَامِلَةٌ نَّاصِبَةٌ}</span> ... مُجْهَدَةٌ بِالعَمَلِ وَالتَّعَبِ فِي النَّارِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَصْلَى نَارًا}</span> ... تَدْخُلُ نَارًا، وَتُقَاسِي حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَامِيَةً}</span> ... شَدِيدَةَ التَّوَهُّجِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آنِيَةٍ}</span> ... شَدِيدَةِ الحَرَارَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَرِيعٍ}</span> ... نَبْتٍ خَبِيثٍ ذِي شَوْكٍ، لَا تَرْعَاهُ الدَّوَابُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِسَعْيِهَا}</span> ... لِعَمَلِهَا بِالطَّاعَةِ فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَاغِيَةً}</span> ... لَا كَلِمَةَ لَغْوٍ وَاحِدَةً، وَلَا نَفْسًا تَلْغُو وَتَهْذِي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَارِيَةٌ}</span> ... مُتَدَفِّقَةٌ بِالمَاءِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّوْضُوعَةٌ}</span> ... مُعَدَّةٌ لِلشَّارِبِينَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَمَارِقُ}</span> ... وَسَائِدُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبْثُوثَةٌ}</span> ... بُسُطٌ كَثِيرَةٌ مَفْرُوشَةٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُطِحَتْ}</span> ... بُسِطَتْ، وَمُهِّدَتْ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمُصَيْطِرٍ}</span> ... بِمُتَسَلِّطٍ تُكْرِهُهُمْ عَلَى الإِيمَانِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
